(Jesus warning about HELL FIRE):

if thy hand causes you to sin,

cut it off:





it is better

that never shall be quenched:





Where their worm dieth not,

and the fire is not quenched.

familiar with the smoldering fires that always burned there.





***(((Obedience))) and (((self-control))) are
necessary to overcome sin.








***The longing of the disciples
for greatness needed to be reshaped according to God's purposes.

snippet.textDisplay:
I have some suggestions.

First, I would like if they made a co-op mode (2 characters for any player and 1 character for the other player // Or one character for each player). It could be online or against CPU (inside some a new mode).

Second, I think it should be possible to choose all the characters at once in the tournament mode. It is very boring have to back to the character screen between each fight.

Third, they should introduce a new mode, in which each player could choose 10 characters at once. The fight would be 3 x 3 yet, but if one character is down, the respective next would take her place immediately, until the end. It would be awesome.

OMFG. YES. FINALLY. FINALLY. FUCKING FINALLY. I dropped this game because I wasn't getting my Kefla. And now she's FINALLY HERE. I'm definitely gonna start playing this game again. She was literally all I fucking wanted for two entire seasons of DLC.

As for Goku, UI Goku looks op. Like, I honestly didn't expect them to put it in there, because it's such an op form. But they probably still nerfed it so ppl can still have a chance. I mean, I guess as long as the player controlling UI Goku doesn't have UI, then it should be doable. LOL.
